name: Enfeeble
desc: Weakens an enemy unit, reducing its physical damage.

name: Rip Tide
desc: The Naga Siren and her images hit all nearby units with a damaging wave of water that lowers armor for 8 seconds.

name: Great Cleave
desc: Sven strikes with great force, cleaving all nearby enemy units with his attack.

name: Dispersion
desc: Damage done to Spectre is reflected on her enemies, leaving her unharmed. The effect lessens with distance.

name: Kraken Shell
desc: Thickens Tidehunter's hide to passively block a portion of any incoming physical attack damage. The hide also removes negative status effects if the damage taken crosses a threshold. Does not stack with items that provide Damage Block. DISPEL TYPE: Strong Dispel

name: Conjure Image
desc: Creates an illusion of Terrorblade that deals damage.

name: Wall of Replica
desc: Raises a wall of warping light that slows and creates replicas of any enemy hero who crosses it. Enemy replicas serve at the Dark Seer's will. Replicas last until they are destroyed, or until the wall's duration ends. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

name: Feast
desc: Lifestealer's attacks damage enemies and heal himself for a percentage of his target's current health.

name: Dragon Blood
desc: The life blood of the Dragon improves health regeneration and strengthens armor.

name: Dream Coil
desc: Creates a coil of volatile magic that latches onto enemy Heroes, stunning them for 0.5 seconds and damaging them.  If the enemy hero stretches the coil by moving too far away, it snaps, stunning and dealing additional damage. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.
